# simplex-engine

Read **AGENTS.md** for commands, architecture map, and MVP priorities.

- Python 3.13+, `uv sync`, tests in `tests/` only.
- Minimal diffs; match existing patterns in `simplex/`.
- Run `uv run ruff check simplex/ tests/` and `uv run pytest tests/ -q` before done.
- Use MCP tools (`health_check`, `world_probe`) when enabled — do not guess project state.
- No git commits unless the user requests them.
- Chunk indices ≠ world blocks; chunk size is 16×16×16.
